    <text id="B0389T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>McDonnell follows up on a lumber purchase intended for school desks in
                Staunton.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R.F. &amp;
                        A.L.</abbr><lb/>Head <abbr expan="Quarters">Qrs.</abbr> 9th Sub <abbr
                            expan="District">Dist.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient">Mr. Thos. P. Jackson<lb/>Agent<lb/>Staunton, <abbr
                            expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-12-04"><abbr expan="December">Dec</abbr> 4t/67</date>
                        <name type="place">Winchester, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>During the month of October last 3000 <abbr expan="feet">ft</abbr> Lumber was
                    purchased at Staunton for the manufacture of Desks for schoolhouse at that
                    place. You will please report, without delay, the number of Desks manufactured,
                    and consider yourself responsible for their safety. You will also enclose with
                    said report your receipt for the number of Desks made.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very Respectfully<lb/>Your <abbr expan="Obedient">Obedt</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Servant">St</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>John A. McDonnell<lb/><abbr expan="Captain">Capt.</abbr> &amp; <abbr
                            expan="Sub Assistant Commissioner">S.A.C.</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
